title: Valar Rereadis: TWOIAF - The Free City of Lys
description:
Valyrian connections past & present, Varys, Salladhor Saan and his ancestors, the Black Swan and Coryanne Wylde, Saera Targaryen, the Rogares, Lynesse Hightower. Find out why Lys is a lot like the Valyrian mafia, and whether Dany/Tyrion will go there.
